@startuml
!include ../../../images/common-sequence.iuml

title Client Device — Provisioning Flow

participant "Client\nFirmware" as Client
participant "Controller\nSoftAP" as AP
participant "Controller\nHTTP API" as API
participant "EEPROM" as EE

Client -> Client : boot with no stored config
Client -> Client : scan WiFi for SSID\n"FireFly-Provisioning" (exact match)
Client -> Client : read BSSID from scan result
Client -> Client : compute WPA2 password:\nnibble-interleave(BSSID)\ne.g. A1:B2:C3:D4:E5:F6 → A6B5C4D3E2F1
Client -> Client : set TX power to minimum\n(0 dBm / 1 mW)

Client -> AP++ : connect WPA2 using derived password
AP --> Client-- : connected (192.168.4.x via DHCP)

Client -> API++ : GET /api/provisioning/nonce
API --> Client-- : 200 { "nonce": 3819273645 }

Client -> API++ : GET /api/provisioning/client\nmac-address: {own MAC}\nx-nonce: 3819273645

alt MAC not registered on Controller
    API --> Client-- : 404 Not Found
    Client -> Client : retry or enter error state
else nonce invalid or already used
    API --> Client-- : 401 Unauthorized
    Client -> Client : retry or enter error state
else success
    API --> Client-- : 200 { name, mac, wifi, mqtt, hid config, uuid, ... }
    Client -> EE++ : store WiFi SSID + password
    Client -> EE : store MQTT host + port + credentials
    Client -> EE : store HID (button) configuration
    Client -> EE-- : store UUID
    Client -> Client : reboot into normal mode
end

@enduml
